message.body: Hello Fawkes17!
Fawkes17 how are you?
I'm doing good. How about yourself?
Great! How did you choose your username?
I was wondering whether "Fawkes" was anon-related
Yeah, it's anon. It used to be my username when I was a kid :P I figured let's bring Fawkes back to life again. Are you a Penn student/alumnus?
No, went to schools around here but not Penn. You?
I graduated from Penn last year. What was your major in school?
Short version: English, 1 yr psych grad school, then med school. You?
Interesting. I did my Master's in Chemical Engineering. Currently working in a startup in the SF Bay area. You still in school, or did you graduate?
I graduated but I'm still applying to residencies. Studying for boards now. Startup sounds fun!
Well, it is a lot of fun! But it's a lot of work too. Not complaining, though. I like it! Do you stay in the Philadelphia area?
Yes, I'm in the western 'burbs. So many resources + things to do here, I feel blessed.
(1/2)I mostly stayed in University City when I was there. Hung out in Center City often, but I have no idea what the western part of Philly looks like. Apart
(2/2)from what's west of 45th St, that is, which isn't exactly great. Have you ever lived outside of Philly?
Born in Chicago
Grew up in central PA
Went to school in Pittsburgh for a few yrs
But mostly have lived in PA
Where r u from originally?
